Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.00,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:07.40,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš, An-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:08.77,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohni si a jedz.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:17.03,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:22.10,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.31,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:26.92,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagino.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:29.59,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:32.80,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... sa ešte nestretneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:38.24,RAINBOW Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem s nimi stráviť viac času.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:54.18,log1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(446,123)}AKT uvádza
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.35,log2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(446,123)}AKT uvádza
